MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-1724. State v. Knotts.

Mercer App. No. 10-94-22. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Mercer County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective October 8,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
